Readability Test </a> - 
Free online test tool from JuicyStudio - enter URL and site will assess 
readability based on Gunning Fog, Flesch Reading Ease, and Flesch-Kincaid 
reading level algorithms.  
</p> 

<!-- [4/10/22 ] -->
