Runscope Radar </a> -
API test automation service from Broadcomm (formerly CA Technologies, formerly Runscope Inc.) for automated testing and 
monitoring of APIs and backend services.  Build tests that verify services are returning expected data 
and receive notifications when things go wrong. Script Engine uses JavaScript for constructing 
customized API tests and validating API responses.  Multipleworldwide monitoring locations available.  
</p>

