SOAPSonar </a> -
Web services client simulation for service testing - for functional, automation, performance, 
compliance, and security testing; from CrossCheck Networks. 
Flexible Test Types - JSON, SOAP, XML, EDI, Batch, REST, etc - all variable-enabled 
and can be linked together for complex business scenario testing.  Automation framework for creation and 
enforcement of rules for assessing pass/fail characteristics of each transaction - includes database and 
environment.  Concurrent Virtual Clients - independent loading agents aggregate statistics for througput, 
latency, and TPS. Ramp-up, ramp-down, and weighted scenarios. Vulnerability Analysis includes dynamic 
XSD mutation security testing with automatic boundary condition testing. Risk assessment and risk
mitigation extensible rule framework.  Available as free personal edition, or enterprise edition.
</p>


