IETester </a> -
Free browser compatibility checker from Core Services, for Microsoft Internet Explorer Versions 
from 5.5 to 11.    WebBrowser that allows you to have the Trident rendering and 
javascript engines of IE11, IE10, IE9, IE8, IE7 IE 6 and IE5.5 on Windows 8, 7, Vista 
and XP, as well as the installed IE in the same process. 
