current versions back to 5.5, as seen from a high speed datacenter located 
in Germany. Just type in a URL.  Able to process a large number of capturing jobs in parallel 
and in realtime, making for fast service.  Targeted to web designers working on Mac and Linux, 
enabling verification of web designs natively on IE versions without the need to have Windows 
PCs.  From GEOTEK Netzwerkservice Berlin. 
</p>

