Run tests from browser, in Node.js, or against many browsers & platforms at the same time with the 
Intern test runner.  Get full code coverage reporting.  Can be used to test Web pages generated by 
server-side languages (like Java, PHP, or Ruby), native or hybrid iOS, Android, and Firefox OS applications,
