mitmproxy</a> - 
Downloadable Open source interactive HTTPS proxy; for debugging, testing, privacy measurements, and 
pen testing; can be used to intercept, inspect, modify and replay web traffic 
such as HTTP/1, HTTP/2, WebSockets, or any other SSL/TLS-protected protocols. Command
line interface, web interface, and python API available.  For Win or Linux. 
</p>


<!-- [4/10/22 ] -->
<p class="webtool">
