<!-- [12/29/20 ] -->
<p class="webtool">
<a href="https://portswigger.net/burp/">
Burp Suite </a> - 
An integrated web app security testing platform from PortSwigger Ltd, written in Java. 
Its various tools work together to support the entire testing process, 
from initial mapping and analysis of an app's attack surface, through to 
finding vulnerabilities.  Can combine advanced manual techniques with 
state-of-the-art automation, to enable faster and more effective security testing.
Key components include: An intercepting Proxy, which lets you inspect and modify traffic between your 
browser and the target application; an application-aware Spider, for crawling content and functionality; 
an advanced web application Scanner, for automating the detection of numerous types of vulnerability; 
an Intruder tool, for performing powerful customized attacks to find and exploit unusual vulnerabilities; 
more. Extensible, allowing writing of custom plugins.  Free and $paid versions; free 
version has manual tools only.  
</p>


