<!-- [4/10/22 ] -->
<p class="webtool">
<a href="https://www.crazyegg.com/">
Crazy Egg </a> - 
Web usability monitoring/analysis tool from Crazy Egg, Inc.  Heatmaps, scrollmaps, and other 
visual reports show exactly how users are responding to elements on your site.  Crazy Egg 
records the entire user session, and then enables understanding of general patterns of how 
people browse your site.  Provides information on areas of customer frustration, 
like form glitches or confusing navigation.   See in real time how people are interacting 
with your product or checkout pages.   Dive into particular audience segments like New, 
Mobile, or Most Active visitor.  Capabilities also include an A/B Test interface that makes 
easy to pick a goal, map a desired website action to that goal, monitor results,
and once a winning variant is detected, more traffic is sent to that winner automatically,
maximizing conversions without having to waste any traffic.
</p>


<!-- [4/10/22 ] -->
<p class="webtool">
