Amazon CodeGuru </a> - 
Automated tool from Amazon.  CodeGuru Reviewer for Java and Python uses machine learning and automated 
reasoning to identify critical issues, security vulnerabilities, and hard-to-find bugs during 
application development and provides recommendations to improve code quality.  CodeGuru Profiler 
helps developers find an application’s most expensive lines of code by helping them understand 
the runtime behavior of their applications, identify and remove code inefficiencies, improve 
performance, and significantly decrease compute costs.
</p>


